.weather_block
    display: flex
    flex-direction: column
    justify-content: space-between
    position: relative
    height: 385px
    .weather_container
        border-right: 1px solid #2F4F4F
        height: 100%
        .weather_now
            display: none
            .weather_temp 
                font-size: 70px
                margin: 20px 20px 0 20px
            .weather_cloudly
                display: flex
                .weather_cloudly-icon  
                    margin: auto
                    height: 175px
                    opacity: 1
            .weather_city
                display: flex
                justify-content: space-between
                align-items: center
                margin: 12px 12px
                .weather_like-button
                    position: relative
                    width: 20px
                    height: 20px
                .weather_like-button::before,
                .weather_like-button::after
                    position: absolute
                    content: ""
                    width: 16px
                    height: 27px
                    top: -5px
                    background-color: #FFA07A
                    border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0
                    transform: rotate(-45deg)
                    transform-origin: 0 100%
                .weather_like-button::after
                    right: 20px
                    transform-origin: 100% 100%
                    transform: rotate(46deg)
                .weather_like-button::before
                    right: 5px
        .weather_details
            display: none
            height: 100%
            .weather_city-name
                margin: 36px 17px
            .weather_city-info
                margin: 0px 17px
                .info
                    font-size: 24px
                    padding: 6px 0px
                    opacity: 0.9
                    span
                        font-size: 24px
                        opacity: 0.75
        .weather_forecast
            display: none
            .weather_city-name
                margin: 36px 17px 0 17px
            .weather_forecast-cards 
                height: 270px
                overflow: hidden
                overflow-y: scroll
                .forecast_card 
                    border: 1px solid #2F4F4F
                    margin: 9px 17px
                    padding: 6px 10px
                    .forecast_card-date
                        display: flex
                        justify-content: space-between
                        margin: 0 0 30px 0
                        .date,
                        .time
                            font-size: 19px
                    .forecast_card-weather
                        display: flex
                        justify-content: space-between
                        align-items: center
                        .forecast_card-temp
                            opacity: 0.8 
            .weather_forecast-cards::-webkit-scrollbar
                width: 3px
            .weather_forecast-cards::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb
                background-color: rgba(47, 79, 79, 0.5)
        .active-window
            display: contents
    .weather_tabs
        display: grid
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr
        .tab
            border: 1px solid #2F4F4F
            border-right: none
            border-bottom: none
            background-color: #ffffff
            padding: 10px 15px
            text-align: center
            cursor: pointer
        .now
            border-left: none
        .forecast
            border-right: 1px solid #2F4F4F
        .tab:hover
            background-color: #2F4F4F
            color: white 
        .active-tab
            background-color: #2F4F4F
            color: white 
 
.weather_city-name
    color: #2F4F4F
    font-size: 30px
